---
/**
 * @fileoverview Email Confirmation Success Page
 *
 * Static success page displayed after successful email confirmation.
 * User is redirected here from the /api/auth/confirm endpoint.
 *
 * @module pages/confirm/success/index
 * @see {@link module:pages/api/auth/confirm} - Redirects here on success
 * @see {@link module:pages/confirm/error/index} - Error counterpart
 * @see {@link module:pages/login/index} - CTA destination
 *
 * ## Route
 *
 * `/confirm/success/` - Public, no parameters
 *
 * ## User Flow
 *
 * ```
 * 1. User clicks confirmation link in email
 * 2. /api/auth/confirm validates token
 * 3. Redirect to this page on success
 * 4. User clicks "Log In Now" button
 * ```
 *
 * ## UI Elements
 *
 * - Success icon (checkmark)
 * - "Email Confirmed!" heading
 * - Confirmation message
 * - "Log In Now" CTA button
 *
 * @author How To Win Capitalism Team
 * @since 1.0.0
 */
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Email Confirmed | How To Win Capitalism</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-bg: #ffffff;
      --color-text: #202122;
      --color-text-muted: #72777d;
      --color-primary: #0645ad;
      --color-border: #a2a9b1;
      --color-success: #0a7a0a;
      --color-success-bg: #e6f4e6;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--color-bg);
      color: var(--color-text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    header {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .site-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-text);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .site-title:hover {
      color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    main {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .success-container {
      max-width: 500px;
      padding: 3rem;
      background: var(--color-success-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-success);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .success-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--color-success);
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--color-text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .login-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      background: var(--color-primary);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .login-button:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <a href="/" class="site-title">How To Win Capitalism</a>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="success-container">
      <div class="success-icon">âœ“</div>
      <h1>Email Confirmed!</h1>
      <p>
        Your email address has been verified successfully.
        You can now log in to your account.
      </p>
      <a href="/login/" class="login-button">Log In Now</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
